NOTICE: The cross-session wake mechanism in this project (a Copilot CLI
extension that calls the SDK's session.send() from a per-session poll loop)
was learned from and is inspired by htekdev/agent-mesh
(https://github.com/htekdev/agent-mesh), also MIT licensed. agent-relay is an
independent reimplementation — not a fork — built around pluggable seams.
